## üîÑ Implementation Process

1. **Component Creation Decision Tree**:
   ```
   Is this functionality already implemented?
   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ YES ‚Üí Can existing code be reused directly?
   ‚îÇ         ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ YES ‚Üí Reuse existing code
   ‚îÇ         ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ NO ‚Üí Can it be enhanced to meet requirements?
   ‚îÇ               ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ YES ‚Üí Enhance existing code
   ‚îÇ               ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ NO ‚Üí Justify new implementation
   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ NO ‚Üí Is there a similar pattern elsewhere?
           ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ YES ‚Üí Adapt existing pattern
           ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ NO ‚Üí Create new based on project standards
   ```

2. **Troubleshooting Map**:
   ```
   Issue detected
   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Build error
   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Type error ‚Üí Check types.ts and component props
   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Module error ‚Üí Check import/export statements
   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Config error ‚Üí Check next.config.js and environment
   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Runtime error
   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Data fetching ‚Üí Check API routes and data models
   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Rendering ‚Üí Check component boundaries
   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Auth ‚Üí Check session and token handling
   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Performance issue
       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Slow initial load ‚Üí Check server components
       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Interaction delay ‚Üí Check client component optimization
       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ API latency ‚Üí Check database queries
   ```

